Igisabisho ni igikorwa c'umuntu umwe canke abantu benshi basenga biyerekeza ku Mana Data wa twese. Uwusenga canke abasenga bashobora kuba bisengera ngo Imana Data wa twese Abahezagire, bashobora kuba basengera abandi bantu, ari nk'abarwaye, canke basengera igihugu, mbere n'isi yose. 
